        </style>
        <p class="font-sora text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mx-auto text-center mt-8" style="max-width:70ch;">Looking for the depth behind these answers? Our <a href="/african-grey-parrot-care-guide/">complete African Grey care guide</a> covers the full husbandry routine, and our <a href="/african-grey-parrot-faq/">African Grey FAQ</a> tackles the buyer-and-owner questions this hub doesn't.</p>
        <div class="text-center mt-6">
