        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed text-[15px] mx-auto" style="max-width:70ch;">Tell us about your home and which Grey caught your eye in the form below, and Mark or Teri will reply within 24 hours. Still comparing the two species? Our <a href="/congo-african-grey-for-sale/">Congo Greys</a> and <a href="/timneh-african-grey-for-sale/">Timneh Greys</a> are both ready to meet you.</p>
